{
  "stem": "18778.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were to be supported by the-- a Jewish agency with headquarters in the Bloomsbury House in London.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And each family got a small amount of money for its sustenance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They weren't allowed to work, because at the time, I guess there wasn't enough work for British people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And besides, we weren't supposed to be staying there for any length of time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was June 1939, OK?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After three months in York, my father felt that nothing's happening in York.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wanted to get out of England.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our papers, meanwhile, had-- were on their way via Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he felt that we've got to be closer to where things are happening in London.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we-- we thanked the Rowntree family very kindly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were Quakers, and they were so generous to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we left for London.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In London, we got a room with a family in Stamford Hill, a Jewish quarter of London.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A lot of Orthodox Jews lived in that neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think we arrived in London perhaps the end of August.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was the end of August.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "On September 1, the Germans invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All the schoolchildren in London were ordered to their schools to their schoolyards, and they wanted to evacuate all the children with their schools out of London.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, we had just gotten there, and the neighborhood school was the Jewish Secondary School of London, a very fine school, very Orthodox school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were-- we were supposed to pack up clothes for several days, and the nice ladies along the way gave us food packages and-- and snacks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the older kids-- I was then 11-- and the-- the older teenagers kept us entertained in the schoolyard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this went on for three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
